Business Brief -- VF Corp.:
   Apparel Maker Plans to Sell
   Factory Outlet Centers
Lawrence R. Pugh, chairman of VF, said in a statement that
the move "will allow us to concentrate on merchandise
selection and store operations rather than real estate
development."
   Outlet Properties Corp. was recently formed by North-South
Management Corp., a North Carolina developer of Carolina
Pottery outlet shopping centers in the Southeast. Closing is
subject to completion of certain actions by Outlet
Properties, VF said. Officials of VF couldn't be reached for
further comment.